    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301940/extras/06dee1321d9ae6473518aa017af1a8b4.poster.avif?t=1758656220\" width=800 height=163 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301940/extras/06dee1321d9ae6473518aa017af1a8b4.webm?t=1758656220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301940/extras/1ad88dd01b3a608d7aec385717c71546.avif?t=1758656220\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301940/extras_big/1ad88dd01b3a608d7aec385717c71546.avif?t=1758656220 width=800 height=135 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BLOW-UP is a single-player first person movement shooter campaign inspired by the best shooters around the Y2K era, reimagining classic action with frantic and dynamic gameplay, along with a modern take on retro graphics and a visually striking “colorful gore” aesthetic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301940/extras/9e413ae20dc11a5d86b91d8435421754.poster.avif?t=1758656220\" width=800 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301940/extras/9e413ae20dc11a5d86b91d8435421754.webm?t=1758656220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301940/extras/9e413ae20dc11a5d86b91d8435421754.mp4?t=1758656220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301940/extras/0e6bab33a5e7c51d0ac11abc085e3e65.avif?t=1758656220\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301940/extras_big/0e6bab33a5e7c51d0ac11abc085e3e65.avif?t=1758656220 width=800 height=135 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your objective is to beat the 20 stages the game has to offer as fast as possible, each one will introduce new tools that will aid your quest of vengeance, but also new challenges to overcome.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301940/extras/85f7c8f444433b1ec0ef8b2bab92f4df.avif?t=1758656220\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301940/extras_big/85f7c8f444433b1ec0ef8b2bab92f4df.avif?t=1758656220 width=800 height=135 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put yourself in the circuit board of the M098 Barbara, a 3 meter tall industrial robot rewired by Ann, the last human alive, to avenge humanity from the alien race that has destroyed Earth. Use any means necessary to violently deny the military occupation the aliens have established on Earth’s debris.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301940/extras/a4ce346c2a42ba51a1822261d9f10724.poster.avif?t=1758656220\" width=800 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301940/extras/a4ce346c2a42ba51a1822261d9f10724.webm?t=1758656220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301940/extras/a4ce346c2a42ba51a1822261d9f10724.mp4?t=1758656220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301940/extras/a7d4e701c50fe836194b0cb374af4180.avif?t=1758656220\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301940/extras_big/a7d4e701c50fe836194b0cb374af4180.avif?t=1758656220 width=800 height=135 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 weapons, each one with an alternate fire mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brutal melee combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Movement mechanics that are also lethal for enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 stage replayable campaign</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secrets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 bosses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Infinite wave mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2D cutscenes</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301940/extras/baad73fe184b5334e6dc31b27bea8576.poster.avif?t=1758656220\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301940/extras/baad73fe184b5334e6dc31b27bea8576.webm?t=1758656220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p>",
